<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337000' id='t-337000'>that really wasn't available even a decade ago.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='339000' id='t-339000'>So it allows us to sample these amazing habitats</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='341000' id='t-341000'>that are very far from the surface</span>
