<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378000' id='t-378000'>because knowing how many fish are there is really critical.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381000' id='t-381000'>We can also use satellite tags</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383000' id='t-383000'>to track animals as they move through the oceans.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385000' id='t-385000'>And so for animals that come to the surface to breathe,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='387000' id='t-387000'>such as this elephant seal,</span>
