</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429000' id='t-429000'>Now one of the other things that you may think about</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='431000' id='t-431000'>is that, when you go to the supermarket and you buy things, they're scanned.</span>
