<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='457000' id='t-457000'>Now one of the nicest examples I like to cite on this</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459000' id='t-459000'>is the story of two young women, high school students in New York City,</span>
